under water until they choke

15:17.067 --> 15:18.736
and scrape their chins, right?

15:18.737 --> 15:19.738
Uh...

15:19.739 --> 15:22.076
Okay. All right. [groans]

15:22.176 --> 15:23.345
You know what though?

15:23.446 --> 15:25.315
- I don't need a hundred bucks.
- What?

15:25.316 --> 15:28.021
Yeah, I'll easily
make that much myself.

15:28.022 --> 15:29.356
Over a few decades.

15:29.357 --> 15:31.194
Maybe we should just
call it, huh?

15:31.195 --> 15:32.865
Oh, really? [stammers]

15:32.965 --> 15:35.035
- You want to leave?
- Yeah, I think I'm good

15:35.036 --> 15:36.204
on ocean stuff for now.

15:36.205 --> 15:38.208
It's big, it's dumb. I get it.

15:38.209 --> 15:41.114
