16:08.202 --> 16:09.772
We're smart. We're smart-ers.

16:09.872 --> 16:10.774
Uh-huh. Yup.

16:10.874 --> 16:12.176
They're all gonna die.

16:12.177 --> 16:13.378
I mean, hopefully not.

16:13.379 --> 16:15.350
They're gonna die,
they're gonna die.

16:15.450 --> 16:17.888
They might make it,
but they'll be traumatized.

16:17.889 --> 16:19.525
[Bob sighs]

16:22.163 --> 16:23.666
[noisemaker blows]

16:25.103 --> 16:26.873
- What?
- Well,

16:26.973 --> 16:28.274
I think I'm gonna head out.

16:28.275 --> 16:29.978
- Happy birthday, Teddy.
- Oh.

16:29.979 --> 16:31.982
Yeah, I'm gonna shove off, too.

16:31.983 --> 16:33.185
Happy birthday, Teddy.

16:33.186 --> 16:35.856
Yeah, thanks for having us?

16:35.857 --> 16:37.427
I didn't, uh...

16:37.528 --> 16:38.764
Yup. [groans]

16:38.864 --> 16:40.199
Uh... uh, wait.

16:40.299 --> 16:41.669
Uh, we haven't
had ice cream yet.

16:41.769 --> 16:44.074
You get free ice cream
on your birthday, right?

16:44.174 --> 16:45.375
What? No, no.

16:45.376 --> 16:47.379
Just Teddy gets
free ice cream, or...

16:47.380 --> 16:49.818
All of you.
You-you all get free ice cream.

16:49.819 --> 16:51.255
I'd stay for
a little soft serve.

16:51.355 --> 16:53.258
I'd stay for a lot
of soft serve.

16:53.259 --> 16:55.129
And sprinkles?
I mean, not-not a deal-breaker,

16:55.229 --> 16:56.297
but if you have 'em...

16:56.298 --> 16:57.801
