17:38.349 --> 17:39.652
- Whose kids are those?
- I don't know.

17:39.752 --> 17:41.789
You know where
you don't die of drowning?

17:41.923 --> 17:44.159
On the land.
There's a 99% chance

17:44.160 --> 17:47.032
