18:21.201 --> 18:22.469
for our third wave.

18:22.470 --> 18:24.407
What? So now
you're fine with dying?

18:24.408 --> 18:27.180
You know, Jamiroquai
and Mark Twain also said,

18:27.280 --> 18:28.950
um, don't not do fun stuff

18:29.051 --> 18:31.320
'cause your dad
got scared one time.

18:31.321 --> 18:33.324
Look, I'm glad you got me
back in the water,

18:33.325 --> 18:34.794
back on the boogie board.

18:34.795 --> 18:37.767
