and I wanted to quit,

19:29.639 --> 19:32.242
but then I learned from
Dad's many mistakes

19:32.243 --> 19:33.513
and said,
"No, we gotta go back."

19:33.613 --> 19:35.148
- [Bob] We both said it.
- I said it better.

19:35.149 --> 19:36.151
And we rode

19:36.251 --> 19:37.286
<i>our final wave to fourth place,</i>

19:37.287 --> 19:38.690
<i>which is a Belcher first place.</i>

19:38.790 --> 19:40.993
